ivardefs.desc: This allows documentation of any distinct behaviors about how the search parameter is used.  For example, text matching algorithms.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: The name of the search parameter used in the interface.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: The type of value a search parameter refers to, and how the content is interpreted.

properties.desc: Search parameters for implementations to support and/or make use of - either references to ones defined in the specification, or additional ones defined for/by the implementation.
